INSERT INTO jobs (org_id, customer_id, assigned_personnel_id, status_id, title, description, job_type, priority, scheduled_start, scheduled_end, location_address, state, commodity_crop, target_pest, epa_number, application_rate, application_method, chemical_product, re_entry_interval, preharvest_interval, max_applications_per_season, max_rate_per_season, methods_allowed, rate, diluent_ground, generic_conditions) VALUES
(1, (SELECT MIN(id) FROM customers WHERE name = 'Green Valley Farms'), (SELECT MIN(id) FROM personnel), 1, 'Cotton Pest Control - Aphid Treatment', 'Pre-bloom aphid control application for cotton field', 'pest_control', 'high', DATE_ADD(NOW(), INTERVAL 1 DAY), DATE_ADD(NOW(), INTERVAL 1 DAY), '1234 Farm Road, Field A, Bakersfield, CA 93301', 'CA', 'Cotton', 'Aphids (Aphis gossypii)', '100-1234', '0.5 lbs/acre', 'aerial', 'Dimethoate 4EC', '48 hours', '21 days', '3', '1.5 lbs/acre', 'Aerial, Ground', '0.5 lbs AI/acre', '20 gallons water/acre', 'Apply when wind speed is below 10 mph. Do not apply within 100 feet of water bodies.'),
(1, (SELECT MIN(id) FROM customers WHERE name = 'Riverside Orchards'), (SELECT MIN(id) FROM personnel), 2, 'Citrus Fungicide Application', 'Preventative fungicide treatment for citrus grove', 'pest_control', 'medium', NOW(), NOW(), '5678 Orchard Lane, Block 3, Fresno, CA 93650', 'CA', 'Citrus (Oranges)', 'Brown Rot (Phytophthora spp.)', '100-5678', '2.5 lbs/acre', 'ground_boom', 'Copper Hydroxide 50WP', '24 hours', '0 days', '6', '15 lbs/acre', 'Ground, Aerial', '1.25 lbs AI/acre', '100 gallons water/acre', 'OMRI listed for organic production. Apply to foliage and fruit.'),
(1, (SELECT MIN(id) FROM customers WHERE name = 'Mountain View Agriculture'), (SELECT MIN(id) FROM personnel), 3, 'Almond Orchard Fertilization', 'Post-harvest nitrogen application', 'fertilization', 'low', DATE_SUB(NOW(), INTERVAL 7 DAY), DATE_SUB(NOW(), INTERVAL 7 DAY), '9012 Valley Drive, Visalia, CA 93277', 'CA', 'Almonds', 'N/A - Fertilization', 'N/A', '50 lbs N/acre', 'ground_boom', 'Urea 46-0-0', '0 hours', 'N/A', '4', '200 lbs N/acre', 'Ground', '108 lbs product/acre', 'Applied dry, incorporated with irrigation', 'Apply post-harvest. Incorporate with irrigation within 24 hours.');
